data.description:
WOW! Amazing home that has really been taken care of and situated in a Cul De Sac  You can truly see the pride of ownership the moment you walk in. The master bedroom has a cute room off the master that could either be an office or a nursery and the upstairs has a large bonus room with a full bath.
This will Go Quick so schedule your showings
Closing will be with Thomas Santoro PA 1700 Wells Rd #5 Orange Park Fl 32073 trina@santoro-law.com

see documents under document tab

***MULTIPLE OFFERS** please submit your H&B by 6,30pm 5/14/21 to link on offer instructions under document tab
